Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:11.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}還想叫我一起看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:13.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}你知道這是小孩子看的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:15.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}你有沒有羞恥心？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}想清楚吧，小馬迷－－
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}一堆粉紅不噁嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}不要浪費你我時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:21.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}你給我小心一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}可是你竟敢...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:28.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}叫我跟著看...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:31.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}這些娘炮的東西－－
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:34.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}你張口大聲唱！
